Package: cluscov
Type: Package
Title: Clustered Covariate Regression
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2019-05-31
Author: Emmanuel S Tsyawo [aut, cre], Abdul-Nasah Soale [aut]
Maintainer: Emmanuel S Tsyawo <estsyawo@temple.edu>
Description: Clustered covariate regression enables estimation and
        inference in both linear and non-linear models with linear
        predictor functions even when the design matrix is column rank
        deficient. Routines in this package implement algorithms in
        Soale and Tsyawo (2019) <doi:10.13140/RG.2.2.32355.81441>.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: quantreg, MASS, stats, utils
